---
title: Communication / Dynamic Diagram — Main Loop Iteration
---
sequenceDiagram
  participant Main
  participant Map
  participant Director
  participant Controller
  participant RobotAPI
  participant Webots

  loop Each TIME_STEP (32ms)
    Main->>Map: update(irSensorList, robot)
    Map->>RobotAPI: read pos, orientation
    Map->>Webots: irSensor[i].getValue()
    Map-->>Main: (map updated)

    Main->>Director: plan_action(robot, map, controller)
    Director->>Map: getmap()
    Director->>RobotAPI: read pos, orientation
    Director->>Controller: set action / target_orientation
    Director-->>Main: (action queued)

    Main->>Controller: act(robot, map)
    alt action == move_forward
      Controller->>RobotAPI: update_position(orientation)
      Controller->>Webots: setPosition / setVelocity (via move_distance_position)
      Controller->>Map: mark_explored(pos)
    else action == turn_*
      Controller->>RobotAPI: look(direction)
      Controller->>Webots: setPosition / setVelocity (via turn_angle)
    end
    Controller-->>Main: (action cleared)
  end
